VoucherResource Resource

Service for manage all data on Voucher Processing

POST /voucher/get

Request Body
media type data type
application/json VoucherBean (JSON)
application/json VoucherBean (JSON)
Response Body
media type data type
application/json ResultJson (JSON)
application/json ResultJson (JSON)

Example

Request
POST /voucher/get
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
